CREATE TABLE real_estate_properties (
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    country VARCHAR(50),
    city VARCHAR(50),

);

CREATE TABLE investor_profiles (
    investor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    investor_name VARCHAR(50),

    investment_amount DECIMAL(12, 2),

);

CREATE TABLE market_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    potential_investors INT,

    investment_recommendation TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE target_market (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  country VARCHAR,
  city VARCHAR,
  population INT,
  median_income DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE real_estate_properties (
  property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  property_type VARCHAR,
  location VARCHAR,
  price DECIMAL,
  size INT
)

CREATE TABLE investor_details (
  investor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR,
  nationality VARCHAR,
  investment_amount DECIMAL,
  investment_type VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE demographics (
  demographic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age_group VARCHAR,
  gender VARCHAR,
  income_level DECIMAL,
  education_level VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE investments (
  investment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  investor_id INT,

  investment_amount DECIMAL,
  investment_date DATE
